<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA22">
<l>vaṭivār muṭikōṭṭi vāṉavarka ṇāḷuṅ</l>
<l>kaṭiyār malartūvik kāṇum – paṭiyāṉaic</l>
<l>cemmaiyā luḷḷurukic cevvaṉē neñcamē</l>
<l>meymmaiyē kāṇa virumpu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Him with the form that is daily seen by celestials, bowing [their]</l>
<l>shapely crowns [and] strewing blossoms full of fragrance,</l>
<l>directly melting inside, o heart,</l>
<l>desire straightaway to see [him] truly.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
